        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-2">ðŸ’¯</div>
          <div class="font-semibold text-black">Guaranteed Response</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Creators reply to you</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-10 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">1. BECOMING A FAN</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Welcome to Flikk! As a fan, you get unique access to connect directly with your favorite creators. 
          By creating a fan account, you agree to these Fan Terms in addition to our general Terms of Service.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>You must be at least 18 years old</li>
          <li>You must provide accurate account information</li>
          <li>You are responsible for maintaining your account security</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">2. WHAT YOU GET</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">As a Flikk fan, you can:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li><strong>Direct Message Creators:</strong> Send messages directly to your favorite creators</li>
          <li><strong>Guaranteed Responses:</strong> Creators commit to responding to your messages</li>
          <li><strong>Subscribe:</strong> Get ongoing access to exclusive content from creators you love</li>
          <li><strong>Send Tips:</strong> Show appreciation and support to creators</li>
          <li><strong>Unlock Content:</strong> Access exclusive photos and content</li>
          <li><strong>Join Livestreams:</strong> Participate in live sessions with creators</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">3. SUBSCRIPTIONS AND PAYMENTS</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Understanding how payments work:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>Subscription prices are set by individual creators</li>
          <li>Subscriptions automatically renew monthly unless cancelled</li>
          <li>You can cancel your subscription at any time</li>
          <li>Tips and content unlocks are one-time purchases</li>
          <li>All payments are processed securely</li>
          <li>Prices are displayed in Indian Rupees (â‚¹)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">4. REFUND POLICY</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Refunds are handled on a case-by-case basis:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>If a creator fails to respond to your messages, you may request a refund</li>
          <li>Technical issues preventing access may qualify for refunds</li>
          <li>Refund requests should be submitted within 7 days</li>
          <li>Contact <a href="mailto:support@flikk.co.in" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">support@flikk.co.in</a> for refund requests</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">5. FAN CONDUCT</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">To maintain a positive community, you agree to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>Be respectful in all communications with creators</li>
          <li>Not request inappropriate or explicit content (no nudity is allowed on Flikk)</li>
          <li>Not harass, stalk, or threaten creators</li>
          <li>Not share or redistribute creator content without permission</li>
          <li>Not attempt to circumvent payment systems</li>
          <li>Not create multiple accounts to abuse free trials or promotions</li>
          <li>Respect boundaries set by creators</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">6. CONTENT USAGE</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Content you access on Flikk is for your personal viewing only:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>You may not download, copy, or redistribute creator content</li>
          <li>You may not share your account credentials with others</li>
          <li>You may not screenshot or screen record content for sharing</li>
          <li>Violations may result in account termination</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">7. YOUR PRIVACY</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We take your privacy seriously:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>Your messages with creators are private</li>
          <li>Your payment information is securely encrypted</li>
          <li>Your subscription activity is not publicly visible</li>
          <li>See our <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_policy_path, class: "text-pink-500 hover:underline" %> for full details</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">8. ACCOUNT TERMINATION</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Your account may be suspended or terminated if you:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>Violate these Fan Terms or our Terms of Service</li>
          <li>Harass or abuse creators</li>
          <li>Engage in fraudulent payment activities</li>
          <li>Attempt to share or redistribute content</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          You may also close your account at any time. Active subscriptions will continue until the end of the billing period.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">9. CONTACT</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          For fan support and questions:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@flikk.co.in" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">support@flikk.co.in</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <%= link_to fan_registration_path, class: "btn-primary px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold inline-flex items-center space-x-2" do %>
        <span>Sign Up as a Fan</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
        </svg>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <!-- Back Link -->
    <div class="text-center mt-4">
      <%= link_to root_path, class: "inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-black transition-colors" do %>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Back to Home</span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
